Package org.omg.CORBA.TypeCodePackage

Provides the user-defined exceptions BadKind and Bounds, which are thrown by methods in in the class TypeCode.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadKind
    The exception BadKind is thrown when an inappropriate operation is invoked on a TypeCode object.
    Bounds
    Provides the TypeCode operations member_name(), member_type(), and member_label.

Package org.omg.CORBA.TypeCodePackage Description
